backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5564824\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 15, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mmv1702546628362.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mmv1702546628362.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mmv1702546628362.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mmv1702546628362\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Right-to-left (RTL) languages are written from right to left of the screen, such as\n\t\tArabic, Hebrew, and Persian languages. English is a Left-to-right (LTR) language.\n\t\tBi-directional writing supports both RTL and LTR languages simultaneously. By default,\n\t\tbi-directional writing is disabled in Uniface IDE editor. To enable bi-directional writing\n\t\tfor an RTL language, you need to update the usys.ini file.</p>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"mmv1702546628362__step_w8444ab1b5b1b1_w8445ab1b5b1_w8446ab1b5_w8447ab1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Edit the usys.ini file.</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"mmv1702546628362__step_w8448ab1b5b1b3_w8449ab1b5b1_w8450ab1b5_w8451ab1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Under the<code class=\"ph codeph\"> [Widgets]</code> &gt; <code class=\"ph codeph\">SourceEdit</code> widget\n\t\t\t\t\tdefinition, change <code class=\"ph codeph\">bidirectional=off</code> to\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">bidirectional=on</code> as shown below:</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mmv1702546628362_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mmv1702546628362__codeblock_fss_3b5_tzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">;usys.ini\n[widgets]\n...\nSourceEdit=usrcedit(font=procboxfont;language=uniface;indenttabs=on;indentsize=4;indentguides=off;bidirectional=off;)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"itemgroup stepresult\">You can now write both from right-to-left and left-to-right directions.</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5564824\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5564824\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Enabling bi-directional writing for an RTL language Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 15, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Right-to-left (RTL) languages are written from right to left of the screen, such as Arabic, Hebrew, and Persian languages. English is a Left-to-right (LTR) language. Bi-directional writing supports both RTL and LTR languages simultaneously. By default, bi-directional writing is disabled in Uniface IDE editor. To enable bi-directional writing for an RTL language, you need to update the usys.ini file. Edit the usys.ini file. Under the [Widgets] > SourceEdit widget definition, change bidirectional=off to bidirectional=on as shown below: Explain this code ;usys.ini [widgets] ... SourceEdit=usrcedit(font=procboxfont;language=uniface;indenttabs=on;indentsize=4;indentguides=off;bidirectional=off;) Copy You can now write both from right-to-left and left-to-right directions. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}